message.content:
Tēnā koe! Kei te whakapau kaha ahau ki te āwhina i a koe ki ētahi whakaritenga ā-ahuru. Tukuna mai ngā pātai kia whakautu ahau i roto i te reo Māori.

1. Ka whakarite he whakaritenga ā-ahuru ki te whakauru ki tētahi whatunga haumaru:
2. Ka whakahaere i tētahi whakapā mai ki te whatunga haumaru me te whakauru i ētahi whakaritenga whakaurunga:
3. Ka whakatau i te kōwhiringa "Whakauru" ki te whakauru i te wharangi whakauru:
4. Ka whakauru i ētahi mōhiotanga whakaurunga ki ngā āpure whakaurunga:
5. Ka taki whakaurunga ki te whakarite i te kupuhipa whakaurunga:
 
Whakapau kaha ahau ki te āwhina i a koe ki ēnei whakaritenga. Tukuna mai ētahi pātai hei whakautu ahau.
